{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake-auto, ament-cmake-gtest, ament-lint-auto, ament-lint-common, can-msgs, lifecycle-msgs, rclcpp, rclcpp-components, rclcpp-lifecycle }:
